getLfAlgo

LoadflowAlgorithm getLfAlgo()
Returns the value of the 'Lf Algo' container reference. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Lf Calculator'.

If the meaning of the 'Lf Algo' reference isn't clear, there really should be more of a description here...

reference to the parent LF algorithm object, containing the object.

Returns:
the value of the 'Lf Algo' container reference.
